USE_0030|I-131 sodium iodide imaging|Which common use is correct?|Whole-body imaging for differentiated thyroid cancer after thyroidectomy or therapy|I-131 can be used for whole-body imaging in differentiated thyroid cancer, though I-123 is preferred for many diagnostic thyroid imaging scenarios.|2|thyroid_cancer_wbi
